projects.name: SOCA: AI-Powered Task Management System with Generative Text for Automated Subtask Generation
projects.description: This is a website that can manage your every day task and chunk the task in manageable subtasks and suggest task to be done for user. The website has login and registration authentication with gmail. User can add, edit, remove and mark as done the tasks.

projects.name: Library Course-Based Computer Usage Monitoring System
projects.description: Developed a user monitoring system specifically for the library's computer section. This system tracks the number of computer users based on their enrolled courses, providing valuable insights into departmental resource utilization. The system exports this data as spreadsheets for easy analysis and reporting.

projects.name: My Sparky Mate
projects.description: We designed and developed a comprehensive website for My Sparky Mate, an Australian-based electrical services company. Built and maintained using WordPress and WPBakery, the site features a modern design and a user-friendly interface. Our work involved significant web design, as well as ongoing fixes and maintenance to ensure optimal performance and a seamless user experience, effectively showcasing My Sparky Mate's full range of services.

projects.name: Autoclave Australia
projects.description: We designed and developed a custom e-commerce website for CISCAL Autoclave Australia, a leading Australian provider of high-quality autoclaves and sterilization equipment. Built on the Shopify platform, the site features extensive web design and utilizes custom Liquid code to tailor its functionality and aesthetics, ensuring a modern and user-friendly interface that effectively showcases their diverse product range. We also integrated the Google Maps API to further enhance the user experience.

projects.name: Extruders Australia
